2026-03-04 12:00:46,027 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Replace inline JS icon maps in _iconmap.pug and nav-plugin.js with flat JSON files (EUI class → icon name). ONE source of truth used by both server-side pug rendering and client-side JS. Eliminates the 3-layer semantic indirection and the manual sync problem between server/client maps.'}
2026-03-04 12:01:01,863 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': 'Architecture: JSON files in html/dui/layout/json/ are the single source of truth.\n\nServer path: _iconmap.pug loads JSON via fn.pug.jsonRead(\'../../layout/json/icons-lucide\'). getIcon() becomes a flat lookup. +icon() mixin unchanged.\n\nClient path: _iconmap.pug injects the loaded map into the HTML as a script variable (e.g. window.__duiIcons). nav-plugin.js reads window.__duiIcons instead of having its own inline copy. $.dui.getIcon() and $.dui.icon() work unchanged.\n\nKey constraints:\n- Pass-through behavior MUST be preserved: unmapped strings (raw Lucide names like "search") must return as-is\n- directIcon overrides (icon-bolt→bolt, icon-nutbolt→nut, etc.) are baked into the flat JSON\n- Bootstrap map exists but is currently unused — include for completeness\n- nav-plugin.js is a plugin file (normally forbidden) but user explicitly authorized this change\n- Must rebuild plugin bundle after nav-plugin change\n\nFiles modified:\n- html/dui/layout/json/icons-lucide.json (NEW — flat EUI→Lucide map)\n- html/dui/layout/json/icons-bootstrap.json (NEW — flat EUI→Bootstrap map)\n- html/dui/layout/_iconmap.pug (REFACTOR — load JSON, simplify getIcon, inject to client)\n- public/dui/js/plugins/nav-plugin.js (REFACTOR — remove inline maps, read from window.__duiIcons)'}
2026-03-04 12:01:10,433 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': 'Create 2 flat JSON files in html/dui/layout/json/:\n\nicons-lucide.json: Pre-resolve every EUI class through iconSemantic→featherMap, with directIcon overrides baked in. Include _default key for fallback. ~105 entries.\n\nicons-bootstrap.json: Same pre-resolution through iconSemantic→bsMap. Bootstrap has no directIcon overrides — those entries resolve through the normal semantic path. ~105 entries.\n\nNOTE: Files were already created prematurely in the previous attempt — review and validate them before proceeding.'}
2026-03-04 12:01:15,975 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': "Refactor _iconmap.pug:\n\nREMOVE: iconSemantic, featherMap, bsMap objects (~250 lines of inline JS)\nADD: Load JSON via fn.pug.jsonRead('../../layout/json/icons-lucide') and fn.pug.jsonRead('../../layout/json/icons-bootstrap')\nSIMPLIFY: getIcon(cls, useBootstrap) becomes a direct map lookup with pass-through for unmapped strings\nKEEP: +icon() mixin unchanged (it just calls getIcon)\nADD: Inject map into page HTML for client-side use — script tag with window.__duiIcons = the loaded lucide map\n\nThe inject is critical — this is how the client-side JS gets the map without having its own copy. The pug template renders once per page load, so the JSON is read from disk once and output as inline JS."}
2026-03-04 12:01:19,359 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': "Refactor nav-plugin.js (lines ~288-348):\n\nREMOVE: Inline iconSemantic object (~32 lines) and featherMap object (~20 lines)\nREPLACE: getIconName(cls) reads from window.__duiIcons instead of inline maps\nKEEP: $.dui.getIcon registration, $.dui.icon() in dui-namespace.js — their API is unchanged\nFIX: Add pass-through for unmapped Lucide names (currently returns '' — should match server behavior and return cls as-is)\n\nThis also fixes the existing inconsistency where directIcon overrides were missing from the client side."}
2026-03-04 12:01:23,263 665862 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 4, 'text': 'Rebuild and verify:\n\n1. Run npm run dui:plugins to rebuild dui-plugins.min.js with the nav-plugin changes\n2. pm2 restart pure4 (pug template changed)\n3. Open browser at http://localhost:3333/?token=p4-agent-dev-token&ui=dui\n4. Check: sidebar menu icons render correctly (these use client-side $.dui.getIcon)\n5. Check: page icons render correctly (these use server-side +icon mixin)\n6. Check console for errors\n7. Navigate to sa_parts and verify icons in toolbar, tabs, buttons\n8. Take before/after screenshots'}
