2026-03-05 08:00:46,767 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 24, 'text': 'Implemented in same changeset:\n- dblclick: fires onDblClickCell(idx, field, value) first, then onDblClickRow(idx, row)\n- Editor auto-open only if no onDblClickRow defined; if defined and returns false, editor skipped\n- contextmenu: binds contextmenu.dgSelect on tbody tr, fires onRowContextMenu(e, idx, row)\n- Not yet browser-tested for dblclick/contextmenu specifically'}
