2026-03-05 10:47:21,796 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'status-dot', 'text': '## Frontend API notes\n\nCurrent bool-dot implementation in combobox-plugin.js (lines 40-82):\n- `ensureBoolDot(sel)` — creates dot span, marks `data-bool`, adds padding (private)\n- `updateBoolDot(sel)` — toggles `bool-yes`/`bool-no` based on selected option text (private)\n- Event wiring: `change` on `SELECT[data-bool]`, `dui:dataloaded`, `dui:contentloaded`\n- Not exposed on `$.dui.fn` or `$.fn` — should become public API\n\nKnown bug: red dots appear on combos that are not yet selected (no selection = shows red). Fix deferred — not part of this task.\n\nWhen generalising, expose a public API like `$.dui.statusDot(el, color)` so any code can add/update a status dot on any element, not just boolean combos.'}
