2026-03-05 10:58:47,624 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': '## Investigation Complete — Full EUI Filegrid Analysis\n\n### Architecture\n\nFilegrid is NOT a standalone component — it\'s a **specialised datagrid initializer** (`$.fn.filegrid`) that calls `$(el).datagrid({...})` with pre-configured columns, toolbar buttons, and event handlers. Plus two datagrid extension methods: `docFiles(key)` and `appFiles(appid)`.\n\n### Data Flow\n\n```\nPage loads record → calls $(\'#partfiles\').datagrid(\'docFiles\', partId)\n  → hits /?_dgrid=y&_sqlid=admin^file_appdoc&_func=get&appdoc={key}&appid={pageId}\n  → returns rows: [{tsid, fname, extn, description, appid, appdoc, revn, uid, type, fclass}]\n```\n\n`appFiles(appid)` variant:\n```\n→ hits /?_dgrid=y&_sqlid=admin^file_app&_func=get&appid={appid}\n```\n\n### Columns (10 fields)\n\n| Field | Title | Visible | Notes |\n|-------|-------|---------|-------|\n| fclass | Type | hidden | |\n| fname | Filename | yes | formatter: icon-{extncls} + filename |\n| appdoc | Doc ID | hidden | shown in admin/files |\n| revn | Rev | hidden | shown in admin/files |\n| tsid | - | hidden | idField |\n| uid | UID | hidden | |\n| type | - | hidden | |\n| extn | - | hidden | used by formatter |\n| appid | - | hidden | |\n| description | Description | yes | |\n\n### Toolbar Buttons (6)\n\n| ID | Icon | Action |\n|----|------|--------|\n| but_select | icon-add | Opens file tree browser modal (#filesel) |\n| but_upload | icon-upload | Opens upload modal (#filewin). If row selected & is grp/pub, asks "Update selected file?" |\n| fl_view | icon-download | Downloads: `/?_func=tsdl&tsid={tsid}&appid={appid}` |\n| fl_viewdoc | icon-monitor | Preview in iframe: `/?_func=tsdl&inline=y&libcon=y&cache=y&tsid={tsid}&appid={appid}` |\n| fl_del | icon-delete | Deletes: `{_func:\'del\', _sqlid:\'admin^file\', tsid, appid}` |\n| but_refresh | icon-reload | `datagrid(\'reload\')` |\n\nfl_view, fl_viewdoc, fl_del are **disabled** until a row is selected.\n\n### Event Callbacks (page hooks)\n\n- `dwap.page.fgOnCheck(idx, row)` — called on row select\n- `dwap.page.fgOnUncheck(idx, row)` — called on row unselect  \n- `dwap.page.fgOnRowContextMenu(evt, idx, row)` — right-click\n- `dwap.page.docfiles` — set to `rows` on load success\n- `dwap._dldata_` — set to selected row data (used by download/preview/delete)\n\n### Side Effects on Load\n\n1. Stores all rows in `dwap.page.docfiles`\n2. Builds comma-separated filenames list\n3. Finds nearest form\'s `_docfiles` hidden input (or creates one)\n4. Sets `_docfiles` value = "file1.ext, file2.ext, ..."\n5. This `_docfiles` value gets submitted with form saves\n\n### Modal Windows (defined in eui/index.pug, lines 266-297)\n\n1. **#docview** — Document preview (iframe)\n2. **#filesel** — File tree browser (tree component loading `admin^dir_tree`)\n3. **#filewin** — Upload form with:\n   - Progress bar (#prog)\n   - File selector (easyui-filebox)\n   - Description (textbox)\n   - Version (textbox)\n   - Upload/Cancel buttons\n\n### Helper: extncls(extn)\n\nMaps file extensions to icon class names:\n- doc/txt/rtf/csv/docx/dot → "doc"\n- zip/tar → "zip"\n- xlsx → "table_excel"\n- ppt → "ppt"\n- pdf → "pdf"\n- png/gif/jpg → "img"\n- xls/xlst/xlsm → "xls"\n\n### Pages Using Filegrid (~20+)\n\nEUI: sa_parts, cp_man, purchase_manager, sa_operators, sa_jobman, contact_man, sa_sorder, quote_man, gauge_man, ncr_main, qp_test, qp_qpman, qualification_man, ci_man, caas_aw95, coc_man, admin/files\n\nDUI (already calling docFiles): sa_parts, cp_man, purchase_manager, sa_operators, sa_jobman, contact_man, sa_sorder, quote_man, + all dqm pages\n\n### Current DUI State\n\n- Skeleton mixin in `display.pug` and `placeholders/filegrid.pug`\n- NO filegrid plugin in `public/dui/js/plugins/`\n- NO docFiles/appFiles methods in datagrid-plugin.js\n- Page scripts call `$(\'#x\').datagrid(\'docFiles\', key)` — currently falls through to EUI shim (or fails silently)'}
2026-03-05 11:00:46,030 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Approach: Compose from existing DUI components\n\nFilegrid is NOT a new component framework — it extends existing ones:\n\n### 1. Datagrid plugin extension (datagrid-plugin.js)\n- Add `docFiles(el, key)` method: loads `/?_dgrid=y&_sqlid=admin^file_appdoc&_func=get&appdoc={key}&appid={pageId}`\n- Add `appFiles(el, appid)` method: loads `/?_dgrid=y&_sqlid=admin^file_app&_func=get&appid={appid}`\n- Both call existing `datagrid('load', url)`\n\n### 2. Filegrid plugin (NEW, thin ~200 lines)\n- `$.fn.filegrid` — initializer that calls `$(el).datagrid({...})` with:\n  - Pre-configured 10 columns (2 visible: fname with icon formatter, description)\n  - Toolbar via +toolbar JSON config (browse/upload/download/preview/delete/refresh)\n  - Row select/unselect handlers (enable/disable toolbar buttons, store `_dldata_`)\n  - onLoadSuccess: build `_docfiles` hidden field, store rows in `$.page.docfiles`\n- Page hooks: `$.page.hook('fgOnCheck')`, `$.page.hook('fgOnUncheck')`, `$.page.hook('fgOnRowContextMenu')`\n- Replace `dwap._dldata_` with `$.page.state.fileSelected` or similar\n\n### 3. Pug mixin (+filegrid in display.pug)\n- Replace skeleton with real mixin that emits a datagrid container div\n- Uses `.easyui-filegrid` class for auto-init (like `.easyui-datagrid`)\n- Minimal markup — the plugin does the heavy lifting\n\n### 4. Layout-level modals (in layout.pug or a new _filegrid.pug partial)\n- **Upload modal**: +modal with form (file input, description, version, progress bar) — uses existing +input mixins\n- **File tree browser modal**: +modal with tree component loading `admin^dir_tree`\n- **Document preview modal**: +modal with iframe\n- Rendered ONCE in the layout, shared by all pages (same as EUI approach)\n\n### 5. File type icon helper\n- `extncls(extn)` function — maps extensions to Lucide icon names (not EUI icon-* classes)\n- Lives in filegrid-plugin.js, exposed as `$.dui.fn.extncls`\n\n### Build order\n1. Add docFiles/appFiles to datagrid-plugin.js (unblocks 20+ page scripts)\n2. Create filegrid-plugin.js (initializer + toolbar + events)\n3. Update +filegrid mixin (real markup)\n4. Add layout modals (upload, tree browser, preview)\n5. Test on sa_parts Attachments tab"}
