2026-03-05 13:02:42,229 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': "## Filegrid Implementation Plan\n\n### Step 1: Data Loading (docFiles)\n- `docFiles()` already exists in datagrid-plugin.js line 1133\n- Filegrid needs to call it when the parent page selects a record\n- Wire up: when filegrid becomes visible/relevant, call `$('#partfiles').datagrid('docFiles', key)`\n\n### Step 2: Upload Handler (integrate into filegrid-plugin.js)\n- Add click handler for `#fg-upload-btn` in the upload modal\n- Build FormData from the modal form (file input + description + version)\n- Append `_sqlid=admin^file`, `_func=add`, `appdoc=<parentKey>`\n- Submit via `fetch()` with `contentType: false` (browser sets multipart boundary)\n- Show progress via `#fg-upload-progress` element\n- On success: reload filegrid data, close modal\n- **Server-side concern**: Express rawBody not captured for multipart — may need middleware addition\n\n### Step 3: Download/Preview/Delete\n- Already wired in filegrid-plugin.js\n- Download: `window.location = /?_func=tsdl&tsid=X&appid=Y`\n- Preview: iframe src with `_func=tsdl&inline=y`\n- Delete: `ajaxget` with `_func=del&_sqlid=admin^file`\n- Verify these work with actual data\n\n### Step 4: Browser verify all operations"}
