2026-03-05 13:16:04,779 1122225 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '**Commit format (v2):**\n```\n<human message>\n\n<file>||<uid>||<notes>\n<file>||<uid>||<notes>\n[mcpp:user=...,task=...,step=...]\n```\n- 5 pipe-delimited fields per file: name|ver|uid|flags|notes\n- ver and flags empty for now (mcpp-dev fills these later)\n- Each changed file gets one line, placed between the message and the [mcpp:...] tag\n- git log --oneline still shows just the subject\n\n**Code changes:**\n- git.py: new FileEntry dataclass, parse_file_lines(), updated build_message() to accept file entries\n- mcpptool.py: _cmd_commit/_cmd_checkpoint use git diff --name-only to get file list, build pipe lines\n- plan_log: show file lines in display when present\n\n**Handoff doc (PROJECT.md):**\n- Placed in ../mcpp-dev/\n- Structured with ## Project, ## Goal, ## Plan, ## Tasks sections for mcpp-plan import\n- References code in mcpp-plan (git.py, mcpptool.py) and pure-git (git.js) for feature parity\n- Covers: file versioning, locking, changelog, rebuild-from-git, build/minify'}
