2026-03-05 13:28:55,109 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'commit-format', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Implement dev_commit with full 5-field pipe-delimited per-file metadata in commit messages'}
2026-03-05 13:29:00,190 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'commit-format', 'kind': 'plan', 'text': "Build on mcpp-plan's commit format (which already has empty ver/flags fields). dev_commit detects changed files, looks up current version in file_track, auto-increments minor, builds pipe lines with all 5 fields populated, appends mcpp-plan's [mcpp:...] tag, commits. Update file_track DB after commit. Reference: pure-git fileCommit() in git.js:204-226, mcpp-plan build_message() in git.py:83-85, _cmd_commit() in mcpptool.py:1477-1518."}
2026-03-05 13:29:00,908 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'file-operations', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Implement file info, locking, and listing tools'}
2026-03-05 13:29:04,805 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'file-operations', 'kind': 'plan', 'text': 'dev_file_show queries file_track + file_changelog for a filepath. dev_file_list shows all tracked files with versions. dev_file_lock/unlock sets/clears the L flag in file_track and records in changelog. dev_file_locked lists all files with L flag. Locked files are blocked from dev_commit. Reference: pure-git locked() in git.js:497-507, infoGet() in git.js:471-479.'}
2026-03-05 13:29:06,138 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'changelog', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Generate changelogs from file_changelog data, with filtering by task, file, version range, or date'}
