2026-03-05 13:29:08,603 1147619 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'rebuild-from-git', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Rebuild file_track and file_changelog tables from git history so the DB is always recoverable'}
