2026-03-05 14:07:12,640 1095779 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': 'Upload working end-to-end. Root causes found:\n1. `_func` must be `upload` (not `add`) — Pure3d fileman.js checks `e.query._func === "upload"`\n2. File must be LAST in FormData — Pure3d\'s busboy parser fires `file` event immediately, and the handler accesses `d.appid.split("^")` which crashes if `appid` field hasn\'t been received yet\n3. Upload must go to Pure3d root `/?_func=upload` with cookie auth (not API key) — the REST API (apiv4.js) doesn\'t have multipart parsing\n4. Cookie obtained by POST to `/login` with `userid=PAC&passwd=Enigma88`, cached 25 min\n\nFiles changed:\n- `lib/endpoints.js`: Added `getRemoteCookie()`, direct HTTPS upload to `/?_func=upload` bypassing apiRequest (no X-Api-Key), fixed `snip()` for non-string values\n- `public/dui/js/plugins/filegrid-plugin.js`: Changed `_func` to `upload`, reordered FormData (fields first, file last), changed file field name from `fname` to `file`'}
