2026-03-05 17:39:19,510 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_new args={'name': 'datagrid-coloff', 'title': 'Datagrid coloff support — per-user column visibility (client-side)', 'steps': ['Pug mixin: emit coloff as data attribute on th/td so plugin can read it', 'Datagrid plugin: read coloff from column config, hide coloff columns by default (display:none on th+td)', 'Datagrid plugin: column picker UI — toggle column visibility, persist to localStorage/cookie', 'Verify editor modal unaffected — coloff columns with editor must remain visible in modal', 'Test with sa_sorder solines grid (has coloff columns with and without editors)']}
2026-03-05 17:39:31,253 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Implement EUI `coloff:true` column property in DUI datagrid. In EUI, coloff columns are hidden from the grid by default but toggleable via a column picker (stored in cookies per user). Since DUI pre-renders pages (same HTML for all users), this must be entirely client-side in the datagrid plugin.'}
2026-03-05 17:39:41,069 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## EUI Reference (eui.extend.js)\n\n### coloff in column chooser (line 1689)\n- When building default visible column list: `if(!memlen && col.coloff!==true) mem.push(col.field)`\n- coloff columns are excluded from the initial cookie — user can toggle them on via column picker\n- Cookie key: `dwap.menu.selected.id + \'^\' + dg.attr(\'id\') + \'^cols\'`\n\n### coloff in formedit (line 2097-2118)\n- NOT checked — all columns with `editor` property are rendered as visible fitem in the form editor dialog\n- Columns WITHOUT `editor` become `input type="hidden"` in the form\n- This means coloff is irrelevant for the editor modal — already correct in DUI\n\n## Implementation Plan\n1. Pug mixin: emit `data-coloff="true"` on `<th>` for coloff columns (JSON config already supports it)\n2. Plugin JS: on init, read coloff from column config, set `display:none` on matching th+td\n3. Plugin JS: column picker dropdown (like EUI\'s colpan) — toggle visibility, persist to localStorage\n4. Editor modal: no changes needed (columns with editor always visible)\n5. Test on sa_sorder solines (has 6 coloff columns, some with editors)'}
