2026-03-05 17:46:02,680 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': "Implement the EUI `columns` method and `coloff` column property in DUI's datagrid plugin. This is the column chooser feature: a checkbox dropdown that lets users show/hide grid columns, with `coloff:true` columns hidden by default. Persistence via localStorage. No pug mixin changes needed — column config (including coloff) is already in JSON and passed to the plugin. The editor modal is unaffected — EUI renders ALL columns with `editor` as visible form fields regardless of coloff/hidden."}
2026-03-05 17:46:17,829 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## EUI Reference (eui.extend.js)\n\n### `columns` method (line 1674)\n- Called by page scripts: `dg.datagrid(\'columns\', $(\'#dgre_tb\'))`\n- Reads cookie `pageId + \'^\' + gridId + \'^cols\'` for saved column visibility\n- If no cookie: builds default list excluding `coloff:true` columns (line 1689)\n- Renders checkbox list into target element, each checkbox toggles `showColumn`/`hideColumn`\n- Saves to cookie on every toggle\n- Supports drag-reorder of columns (via `eui.droplist`)\n\n### `showColumn` / `hideColumn` (line 1755-1766)\n- jQuery EasyUI built-in methods — show/hide columns by field name\n- DUI has these as stubs (no-ops) at lines 1110-1114\n\n### `coloff` (line 1689)\n- Only used in the column chooser default list builder\n- `coloff:true` → excluded from initial visible set (checkbox unchecked)\n- NOT checked in `formedit` — all columns with `editor` are always visible in the form\n\n### `formedit` editor modal (line 2097-2118)\n- `if(e.editor)` → visible fitem with label + input\n- `else` → `input type="hidden"` (carries data silently)\n- `coloff` and `hidden` are irrelevant — only `editor` property matters\n- DUI already handles this correctly\n\n## Implementation Plan\n1. Implement `showColumn(field)` / `hideColumn(field)` in datagrid plugin\n2. Implement `columns` method — checkbox dropdown, coloff defaults, localStorage persistence\n3. No pug changes — JSON config already has coloff, plugin reads it\n4. Editor modal — no changes, already correct\n5. Test with pages that call `.datagrid(\'columns\', ...)` — 20+ DUI page scripts already do\n\n## Affected Files\n- `public/dui/js/plugins/datagrid-plugin.js` — main implementation\n- JSON configs with coloff: sa_sorder_solines, sa_ship_shiplines, quote_man_qlines\n- 20+ page scripts already call `.datagrid(\'columns\', ...)` — currently no-ops'}
2026-03-05 17:46:22,118 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Implement showColumn/hideColumn in datagrid plugin', 'description': 'Replace stubs at lines 1110-1114. Toggle display:none on th and td by data-field attribute.'}
2026-03-05 17:46:28,469 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Implement columns method — checkbox dropdown with coloff defaults', 'description': 'Port EUI columns method (eui.extend.js:1674). Render checkbox list for each column with a title. coloff:true columns unchecked by default. Checkbox toggle calls showColumn/hideColumn. Persist to localStorage keyed by pageId + gridId.'}
2026-03-05 17:46:29,855 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Verify editor modal unaffected by column visibility', 'description': 'Confirm that showColumn/hideColumn only affect grid th/td, not editor modal fitem fields. Columns with editor must always be visible in the modal regardless of coloff/hidden state.'}
2026-03-05 17:46:31,550 1177280 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': "Test with live pages that call .datagrid('columns')", 'description': 'Test sa_sorder solines (6 coloff cols, some with editors), sa_ship shiplines, quote_man qlines. Verify checkbox dropdown renders, coloff cols hidden by default, toggle works, persistence survives reload.'}
