2026-03-07 12:53:13,843 1549321 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Build a searchbox-plugin.js that provides a type-to-search widget for large datasets (thousands of records). Replaces native `<select>` for big-data comboboxes where loading all options into the DOM kills performance.\n\n**User-facing behaviour:** Text input with search icon. User types → debounced request to server → dropdown shows matching results → user picks one. Supports pagination for result sets that exceed a page size.\n\n**Server contract:** Remote Pure3d server already supports pagination via `page` (1-indexed) and `rows` (page size) query params, returning `{total, rows}`. The proxy (`lib/endpoints.js`) forwards these params unchanged.\n\n**Replaces:** The combobox-big-data problem. Instead of loading 5000+ options into a `<select>`, the searchbox fetches only matching records on demand.'}
2026-03-07 12:53:33,998 1549321 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Plan: searchbox-plugin.js\n\n### Research findings\n- EUI searchbox (`public/eui/plugins/jquery.searchbox.js`) is a thin textbox wrapper — delegates all search logic to user callbacks\n- EUI datagrid pagination sends `page` + `rows` params, expects `{total, rows}` response\n- Proxy (`lib/endpoints.js`) forwards `page`/`rows` unchanged to remote server\n- Existing DUI searchbox: skeleton mixin in `html/dui/mixins/input.pug` (lines 619-625), plus `public/assets/js/searchbox-helper.js` shim — both minimal\n- No actual searchbox usage found in current EUI page scripts\n\n### Steps\n\n**Step 1: Design the API surface**\n- Define the plugin options interface (url, queryParams, valueField, textField, pageSize, delay, minChars, onSelect callback)\n- Define how page scripts will use it — must be compatible with EUI `class:\'searchbox\'` pattern in pug mixins\n- Define the DOM structure (input + dropdown container)\n\n**Step 2: Build searchbox-plugin.js**\n- Register via `$.dui.shim(\'searchbox\', ...)`\n- On input (debounced, default 300ms): POST to `_sqlid` endpoint with search term + `page=1` + `rows=pageSize`\n- Render dropdown with results (`textField` displayed, `valueField` stored)\n- Keyboard navigation (up/down/enter/escape)\n- Click-to-select\n- "Load more" or scroll-to-paginate for additional pages\n- Expose: `getValue()`, `setValue()`, `getText()`, `clear()`, `disable()`, `enable()`\n\n**Step 3: Update the searchbox mixin**\n- Enhance skeleton in `input.pug` to emit correct DOM structure\n- Support `data-options` for url, queryParams, valueField, textField, etc.\n\n**Step 4: CSS for dropdown**\n- Positioned below input, max-height with scroll\n- Loading spinner state\n- Highlighted/selected item styling\n- Use DaisyUI classes where possible (dropdown, menu)\n\n**Step 5: Integration test**\n- Add a searchbox to dev/layout.pug test page\n- Wire to an existing `_sqlid` endpoint with many records\n- Verify: type-to-search, pagination, selection, keyboard nav\n\n**Step 6: Bundle and verify**\n- Add to `scripts/build-dui-plugins.sh`\n- Rebuild plugins: `npm run dui:plugins`\n- Verify in browser\n\n### Constraints\n- Server-rendered first: static DOM in pug mixin, JS only for dynamic behaviour\n- Must expose `window.searchbox` or equivalent for legacy page script compatibility\n- Must work with existing proxy architecture — no server changes needed\n- Debounce to avoid hammering the server on every keystroke'}
2026-03-07 12:59:18,112 1549321 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_new args={'title': 'Build searchbox-plugin.js', 'description': "Create the core searchbox plugin: debounced type-to-search, dropdown results, keyboard nav, pagination, standard widget API (getValue/setValue/getText/clear/disable/enable). Register via $.dui.shim('searchbox')."}
