2026-03-07 15:32:11,119 1549321 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'id': 568, 'kind': 'note', 'text': '## Searchbox Filter Drawer — Design Decision (REVISED)\n\n### Context\nThe searchbox needs column-level filtering, similar to EUI\'s qbedef.js pattern where each column can have an `editor` (textbox, combobox, datebox, numberbox) that sends additional query params to the server endpoint.\n\n### Rejected: Left slide-out drawer\nNot enough horizontal room — dropdown already ~700px wide for table, adding 220px drawer risks going off-screen.\n\n### Rejected: Separate modal\nIf modal overlaps the results table, user can\'t see results update when filters are applied.\n\n### Chosen Design: Collapsible accordion above results\nA filter section sits between the dropdown header and the results table. Collapses to a thin toggle bar when closed. When open, pushes results down but user sees immediate effect after Apply.\n\n```\nCollapsed:\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ▶ Filters                                    │ ← thin bar, base-200\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Part ID │ Description │ Class │ UOM │ ...    │\n\nExpanded:\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ▼ Filters                              [×]   │\n│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐          │\n│  │Part Class  ▼ │  │Traceable   ▼ │          │ ← 2-col grid of compact fitems\n│  ├──────────────┤  ├──────────────┤          │\n│  │Product Code  │  │Alias         │          │\n│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘          │\n│                                    [Apply]   │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Part ID │ Description │ Class │ UOM │ ...    │\n│ ...     │             │       │     │        │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Showing 20 of 25 — click for more           │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### JSON Config\nAdds a `filters` array to searchbox JSON config, using same editor format as qbedef.js:\n```json\n"filters": [\n  { "field": "PART_CLASS_ID", "title": "Part Class", "editor": { "type": "combobox", "options": { "data": [...] } } },\n  { "field": "TRACEABLE", "title": "Traceable", "editor": { "type": "combobox", "options": { "data": [...] } } },\n  { "field": "PRODUCT_CODE", "title": "Product Code", "editor": "textbox" },\n  { "field": "ALIAS_DESC", "title": "Alias", "editor": "textbox" }\n]\n```\n\n### Implementation Rules\n- **Server-side first**: Filter section DOM built by pug mixin using +fitem() or compact equivalents\n- **Use existing mixins** where available and workable\n- JS only wires events: toggle open/close, collect filter values, add to queryParams on search\n- Funnel icon or "Filters" text toggles the section\n- 2-column grid layout for compact filter form\n- Combobox editors: native `<select>` for simplicity inside the dropdown\n- Apply button re-queries with filter params merged into queryParams\n- Filter section only rendered if `filters` array exists in JSON config\n- Collapsed by default — thin bar with "▶ Filters" text'}
