2026-03-07 18:59:09,114 1549321 DEBUG mcpp.git running: git commit -m searchbox: create all 14 qbedef JSON configs with _sqlid comboboxes, datebox filters, and auto-init

- Created searchbox JSON configs for all 14 EUI qbedef entries in html/dui/json/
  (part, sorder, job, ship_ids, soref_ids, customer_ids, everslik_ids, gauge_ids,
  caas_aw95, operator, gatepass_ids, po_ids, receipt_ids, opnrefs)
- Every field from every qbedef included — no cherry-picking
- Combobox filters use _sqlid for database-backed lookups (admin^curr, admin^gst,
  vwltsa^custid, inv^vendorid, inv^pn_partclass, vwltsa^depid1, vwltsa^shiftid,
  vwltsa^resourceid, dqm^gaugeType, dqm^department, vwltsa^wocid, vwltsa^productcodeid)
- Inline data only for fixed-code combos (STATUS H/R/C, ACTIVE Y/N, GP_TYPE C/V)
- Added datebox editor type support in input mixin filter rendering
- searchbox-plugin.js: init combobox widgets inside dropdown filters after findDropdown()
  (dataloader-plugin only searches #content, dropdown is moved to document.body)
- Pass url directly to .combobox() init from _sqlid attribute
- Updated docs/dui/searchbox.md with all configs, _sqlid combobox pattern, datebox docs

