2026-03-08 08:32:07,367 1737642 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'id': 648, 'text': '**Implementation (revised):**\n\nNo `autoHide` flag needed. ALL columns start with `coloff` class (hidden). During row iteration, any column with data gets unhidden. Columns that remain empty across all rows stay hidden.\n\n1. **Pug template** — all `<th>` and template `<td>` get `.coloff` class by default\n2. **JS renderResults** — track hidden columns in a Set, unhide (remove coloff) when a cell has data, early-exit when all columns visible\n3. **Reset on new search** — re-add coloff to all headers and template cells, rebuild hidden set\n4. **"Load more"** — carry over hidden set from previous page, continue unhiding'}
