2026-03-08 18:34:10,444 1917971 DEBUG mcpp.git running: git commit -m toolbar mixin: flat flex layout with CSS order for 3-section centering

- Flatten toolbar structure: no wrapper divs, all content as direct children
- CSS order sorts fitems left (order:3) and buttons right (order:100)
- Two flex-1 spacers center inputs between title and buttons
- Size maps: sm/md/lg with distinct text-xs/text-sm/text-base, padding, gaps
- em-based --input-h:2em on .dui-toolbar so inputs scale with font-size
