2026-03-09 07:28:26,091 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'euiextend', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Investigate all overrides/enhancements in public/js/eui.extend.js and determine which are already implemented in the DUI plugin system and which are missing. Incorporate any missing functionality into the appropriate DUI plugins.\n\n## Overrides/Enhancements in eui.extend.js\n\n### Global Utilities (eui object)\n- eui.aliases() — syncs data-alias textbox values\n- eui.table() — builds HTML tables from head/rows data\n- eui.nav() — tab navigation helper\n\n### Parser\n- $.parser.onComplete — custom post-parse hooks (lines 205, 1659)\n\n### Panel\n- $.fn.panel.defaults — clears loadingMessage\n- $.fn.panel.methods — extended methods\n\n### Dialog / Window\n- $.fn.dialog.parseOptions — custom parser\n- $.fn.dialog.defaults — default overrides\n- $.fn.window.defaults — default overrides\n\n### Tabs\n- $.fn.tabs.defaults — default overrides\n- $.fn.tabs.methods — extended methods\n\n### Form (major section)\n- $.fn.form.parseOptions — custom parser (line 316)\n- $.fn.form.defaults — extensive default overrides (line 349)\n- $.fn.form.methods — extended methods (line 491)\n\n### Linkbutton / Switchbutton\n- $.fn.linkbutton.parseOptions — custom parser (lines 623, 635)\n- $.fn.linkbutton.defaults — default overrides\n- $.fn.switchbutton.defaults — default overrides\n\n### Date/Time Widgets\n- $.fn.timespinner.defaults, $.fn.datetimebox.defaults/methods\n- $.fn.datebox.defaults/methods/parseOptions\n\n### Number/Spinner\n- $.fn.numberspinner.defaults — editable:true, min:0, precision:2\n- $.fn.numberbox.methods — extended methods\n\n### Textbox / Validation\n- $.fn.validatebox.defaults/methods/rules — custom validation rules (line 884)\n- $.fn.textbox.defaults.inputEvents — focus handler overrides\n- $.fn.textbox.methods.initValue, parseOptions, extended methods\n\n### Combobox (major section)\n- $.fn.combobox.parseOptions — extensive custom pre-parser (line 965)\n- $.fn.combobox.defaults — default overrides (line 1146)\n- $.fn.combobox.methods — extended methods (line 1230)\n\n### Datagrid (major section)\n- $.fn.datagrid.methods — extended methods (lines 1672, 2346)\n- $.fn.datagrid.defaults — default overrides (line 2319)\n- $.fn.datagrid.defaults.editors — custom editors (line 2589)\n- $.fn.datagrid.defaults.view — view overrides (line 2607)\n\n### Tree\n- $.fn.tree.defaults — default overrides (line 2622)\n- $.fn.tree.methods — extended methods (line 2704)\n\n### Custom Widget: Multibox\n- $.fn.multibox — entirely new widget (line 2781), extends $.fn.combo'}
2026-03-09 07:28:37,917 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'euiextend', 'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Audit DUI plugins for existing coverage\nFor each category in eui.extend.js, check the corresponding DUI plugin to see what\'s already implemented:\n- form-plugin.js ↔ Form section (parseOptions, defaults, methods)\n- combobox-plugin.js ↔ Combobox section\n- datagrid-plugin.js ↔ Datagrid section\n- modal-plugin.js ↔ Dialog/Window section\n- Other plugins ↔ remaining sections (tabs, tree, validation, etc.)\n\n### Phase 2: Classify each override\nFor every override/enhancement, mark it as one of:\n1. **Already in DUI** — equivalent functionality exists in a DUI plugin\n2. **Not needed in DUI** — EUI-specific plumbing that DUI handles differently (e.g. parser hooks)\n3. **Missing, needs porting** — business logic or behaviour that DUI pages depend on but hasn\'t been ported\n\n### Phase 3: Incorporate missing items\nFor each "missing, needs porting" item:\n- Determine which DUI plugin it belongs in\n- Port the logic, adapting to DUI conventions (no EasyUI widget API, use native DOM/DUI patterns)\n- Test on the dev page (sa_parts.pug) or a relevant page that exercises the feature\n\n### Phase 4: Verify\n- Run through key DUI pages to confirm no regressions\n- Confirm ported features work as expected'}
