2026-03-09 07:30:46,351 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': "Produce a classification table for every override in eui.extend.js. Each entry gets one of three labels:\n\n1. **Already in DUI** — equivalent exists in a DUI plugin (note which plugin and where)\n2. **Not needed in DUI** — EUI-specific plumbing (parser hooks, EasyUI widget API shims) that DUI architecture eliminates\n3. **Missing, needs porting** — business logic or behaviour that DUI pages rely on but hasn't been ported yet\n\nFocus areas likely to have gaps:\n- Custom validation rules ($.fn.validatebox.defaults.rules)\n- Combobox pre-parser logic (extensive data-attribute parsing)\n- Datagrid custom editors and inline editing behaviour\n- Multibox widget (entirely custom, may need a DUI equivalent)\n- eui.aliases() if any DUI pages use data-alias"}
2026-03-09 07:30:51,783 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'text': 'For each eui.extend.js category, read the corresponding DUI plugin and check for equivalent functionality:\n\n- form-plugin.js ↔ Form (parseOptions, defaults, methods — lines 316-622)\n- combobox-plugin.js ↔ Combobox (parseOptions, defaults, methods — lines 965-1658)\n- datagrid-plugin.js ↔ Datagrid (methods, defaults, editors, view — lines 1672-2620)\n- modal-plugin.js ↔ Dialog/Window defaults and parseOptions\n- Check for: tabs, tree, validation rules, textbox focus handling, multibox widget\n- Check eui.aliases(), eui.table(), eui.nav() utilities in bundle.js / DUI namespace'}
2026-03-09 07:31:40,862 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 1, 'id': 662, 'text': "For each eui.extend.js category, read the actual code and document what each override/enhancement does — not just that it exists, but its purpose and behaviour.\n\nThen update the task goal notes with a detailed summary of each override's functionality.\n\nCategories to read and summarise:\n- Global utilities: eui.aliases(), eui.table(), eui.nav() — what do they do, who calls them?\n- $.parser.onComplete hooks (lines 205, 1659) — what do they trigger?\n- Panel defaults/methods — what's changed and why?\n- Dialog/Window defaults and parseOptions — what custom behaviour?\n- Tabs defaults/methods — what's extended?\n- Form parseOptions/defaults/methods (lines 316-622) — what custom form behaviour? (major section)\n- Linkbutton/Switchbutton parseOptions/defaults — what's customised?\n- Date/Time widgets defaults/methods/parseOptions — what's changed?\n- Number/Spinner defaults/methods — what's extended?\n- Textbox/Validation defaults/methods/rules/inputEvents (lines 791-962) — what custom rules? What focus handling?\n- Combobox parseOptions/defaults/methods (lines 965-1658) — what does the pre-parser do? (major section)\n- Datagrid methods/defaults/editors/view (lines 1672-2620) — what custom editing, what view changes? (major section)\n- Tree defaults/methods (lines 2622-2780) — what's extended?\n- Multibox widget (lines 2781+) — what is it, how does it work?\n\nAfter reading, update task goal notes with functional summaries for each."}
2026-03-09 07:34:11,589 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'euiextend', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Investigate all overrides/enhancements in public/js/eui.extend.js, determine which are already in DUI, and incorporate missing ones.\n\n## Functional Summary of Each Override\n\n### Global Utilities (`eui` object, lines 10-200)\n- **eui.aliases()** — Copies values from one textbox to another via `data-alias` attributes. Called after form load.\n- **eui.table(head, rows)** — Builds an HTML `<table>` from column definitions (field/title/formatter/style) and row data. Used for ad-hoc table rendering.\n- **eui.colsort(dg, arr)** — Reorders datagrid columns in the DOM to match an array of field names.\n- **eui.droplist(ul, cb)** — Makes `<li>` items draggable/droppable for reordering (used in column chooser).\n- **eui.translate(obj)** — i18n: replaces element text with translation from `dwap.lang` dictionary.\n- **eui.formatValue(target)** — Applies a textbox\'s `formatter` function to its current value.\n- **eui.date(val)** — Extracts date portion (digits and hyphens) from a string.\n- **eui.ref2text(val)** — Converts `^` separators to `.` in reference strings.\n- **eui.currency/integer/number(val)** — Formatting helpers: currency with `$`, integer, fixed-decimal number.\n- **eui.isloading(fid)** — Returns whether a form is currently loading data.\n- **eui.toolbar(els)** — Dynamically builds toolbar items (linkbuttons, combos, etc.) in the panel header.\n- **eui.textPut/textGet(obj/arr)** — Batch set/get textbox values by ID.\n- **eui.sqlid(sqlid)** — Resolves a `_sqlid` reference to a URL, prepending menu root if needed.\n- **eui.navi(cbo)** — Appends forward/back navigation buttons to a combobox.\n- **eui.eventOff/eventOn(obj, type, evt)** — Temporarily disables/re-enables a widget event handler (stores backup with `__` prefix).\n\n### Parser (lines 204-215) — COMMENTED OUT\n- `$.parser.onComplete` — Would iterate datagrids after parse. Currently disabled.\n\n### Panel (lines 218-223)\n- **defaults**: Clears `loadingMessage` (no "Loading..." text).\n- **methods.setIcon**: Adds an icon class to the panel icon element.\n\n### Dialog (lines 225-237)\n- **parseOptions** — COMMENTED OUT (would add `dialog-box` class).\n- **defaults**: Sets `bodyCls:\'dbox\'` on all dialogs.\n\n### Window (lines 240-247)\n- **defaults**: `doSize:true, closable:true, collapsible:false, minimizable:false, maximizable:false, modal:true` — makes windows modal-only by default.\n\n### Tabs (lines 250-309)\n- **defaults.onUpdate** — Translates tab titles via `eui.translate()`, enables buttons on first tab via `butEn()`.\n- **defaults.onUnselect** — Prevents tab switch if `locked`, otherwise triggers `butEn()` for button state management.\n- **methods.onDemand** — Lazy-loads tab content from `<template>` fragments on first select. Calls per-tab callbacks.\n- **methods.enableAll/disableAll** — Enable/disable all tabs at once, optionally selecting one.\n- **methods.lock/unlock** — Prevents/allows tab switching via a `locked` flag.\n\n### Form (lines 312-616) — MAJOR SECTION\n**parseOptions (line 316)**:\n- Sets method to `eui.ajax_method`.\n- `.single` forms: Sets mode to `upd`, asdpx to `s`, builds URL from `_sqlid` attribute, auto-loads if `.load` class present.\n- `.multi` forms: Sets mode to `add`, asdpx to `ax`, disables `.fkey` fields.\n\n**defaults (line 349)**:\n- **onChange** — Tracks changed fields in `opts.changed[]`, adds `.changed` class, fires `changed` event. Skips during loading.\n- **onSubmit** — Blocks submit if read-only, validates form (finds hidden invalid fields in tabs), alerts user.\n- **success** — Parses JSON response, handles `del` mode (reset + reload combo) vs `add/upd` mode (editbox reset or QBE runMode), fires `done`/`success` events, clears change tracking.\n- **onBeforeLoad** — Clears changes, sets `loading` flag.\n- **onLoadSuccess** — Enables/disables form based on read-only state, unlocks tabs, stores fkey value, calls `eui.aliases()`, fires `loadDone` event after 250ms delay.\n\n**methods (line 491)**:\n- **reload** — Reloads form data using its `_sqlid` and current fkey value.\n- **reset** — Resets all field types (not just inputs).\n- **getData** — Returns form data as dictionary via `frm2dic()`.\n- **focusFirst** — Focuses first enabled visible non-readonly input.\n- **unchange** — Clears `.changed` class and resets change tracking.\n- **preload** — Loads data without triggering `onLoadSuccess` (temporarily disables it).\n- **changeFieldName** — Renames all field names/textboxNames via a transform function.\n- **reselect** — Re-selects all comboboxes in the form (workaround for 1.4.1 bug).\n- **enable/disable** — Adds/removes `form-lock` class, unlocks `.fkey` items.\n\n### Linkbutton (lines 618-666)\n- **parseOptions** — Adds double-click prevention: locks button for `clickms` ms (default 2000) after mouseup.\n- **defaults.onClick** — Dispatches `but_add()` / `but_clr()` based on button ID.\n\n### Switchbutton (lines 669-678) — COMMENTED OUT\n- Would set onText/offText to YES/NO.\n\n### Date/Time Widgets (lines 680-776)\n- **timespinner.defaults** — `highlight:1, value:\'12:00\'`.\n- **datetimebox.defaults** — Custom `formatter` (calls `myTime()`), custom `parser` (handles ISO/timezone conversion).\n- **datebox.defaults** — Shared calendar (`#calendar`), custom `formatter` (calls `myDate()`), custom `parser` (handles 6-digit dates, ISO conversion). `postdate/predate` flags with `onChange` validation that blocks future/past dates.\n- **datebox.methods** — `getDate` (parse to Date), `today/month/year` (set or return formatted dates).\n- **datetimebox.methods** — `getTime` (parse datetime to Date).\n- **datebox.parseOptions** — Auto-sets value to today/month start/year start based on `.today/.month/.year` class.\n\n### Number/Spinner (lines 778-788)\n- **numberspinner.defaults** — `editable:true, min:0, precision:2`.\n- **numberbox.methods.set** — Batch-sets numberbox options and re-applies value.\n\n### Textbox/Validation (lines 790-959)\n- **validatebox.defaults** — `deltaX:20` (tooltip offset).\n- **Focus handler / initValue** — COMMENTED OUT (would apply formatter on focus/init).\n- **Validate parser** — COMMENTED OUT (would force multiline).\n- **validatebox.methods.required/editable** — Dynamically set required/editable and revalidate.\n- **textbox.methods.setValidType** — Changes validType on a textbox\'s inner validatebox.\n- **textbox.methods.dropbox** — Enables drag-and-drop file reading into a textbox (reads file as text, validates extension).\n- **Validation rules** (line 884):\n  - `csn` — Comma-separated numbers only.\n  - `neq` — Value must not equal a parameter.\n  - `isJSON` — Must be valid JSON.\n  - `noList` — Always passes (placeholder).\n  - `inList` — Value must match a combobox item\'s text (skips if empty data, not editable, or add-mode).\n  - `sqlsafe` — Only allows letters, digits, hyphens, slashes, dots, backslashes.\n  - `xlsx` — Must end in `.xlsx`.\n  - `file` — No dots, asterisks, or spaces.\n  - `udfLabels` — Strips `{...}` prefix and `*`, then checks length.\n\n### Combobox (lines 961-1654) — MAJOR SECTION\n**parseOptions (line 965)** — Extensive pre-parser:\n- Stores combo as form\'s fkey data.\n- `.first/.last` class: Auto-selects first/last item on load.\n- `.edit` class: Creates inline add/edit dialog for combo items with dynamic fields.\n- `.fit` class: Sets `panelWidth:208`.\n- `.fkey` class: Builds an "edit-wrap" with a validatebox for adding new records, navigation buttons, sqlsafe validation.\n- `.navi` class: Appends forward/back navigation buttons.\n- `cloneSource` option: Clones data from another combobox.\n\n**defaults (line 1146)**:\n- Standard fields: `value/text`, `method:post`, `selectOnNavigation:false`, `validType:[\'inList\']`.\n- `onShowPanel/onHidePanel` — Tracks `clicked` state.\n- `onResize` — Applies icon background to textbox, enables sticky group headers, starts auto-refresh interval.\n- `loadFilter` — Prepends "- ALL -" row for `.all` class combos.\n- `onSelect` — Triggers form load via `formLoad()` method, fires `select` event.\n- `onBeforeLoad` — Builds URL from `_sqlid`, prevents double-loading via `loaded` flag.\n- `onLoadSuccess` — Auto-selects value if `autoload` is set.\n\n**methods (line 1230)** — 20+ custom methods:\n- **paginate/_paginate** — Infinite scroll loading with remote data.\n- **cloneFrom** — Clones combo data from another combobox.\n- **reset** — Resets to `originalValue` if not manually selected.\n- **selected** — Finds and selects the item with `selected:true` in data.\n- **filtertip** — Creates a filter tooltip with checkboxes that modify query params and save to cookies.\n- **delete/append** — Directly manipulate combo items in DOM and data.\n- **sticky** — Makes group headers sticky on scroll.\n- **formLoad** — Core method: when fkey combo selects a value, loads the form with that record.\n- **empty** — Clears all data.\n- **toCombo/toText** — Toggles a combo between dropdown mode and plain text mode.\n- **getField** — Gets a specific field from the selected record.\n- **load** — Extends query params and reloads.\n- **reload** — Reloads with `loaded:false` reset, preserves selection.\n- **find/selectKey/exists** — Search combo data by key-value pair.\n- **reselect** — Unselects and re-selects current value (triggers events).\n- **getRec** — Returns the full data record for current selection.\n- **index** — Navigates to next/previous item (used by nav buttons).\n- **autonum** — Toggles auto-number mode (readonly with auto-generated values).\n- **editbox** — Toggles between combo selection and text input for new record entry.\n\n### Datagrid (lines 1672-2618) — MAJOR SECTION\n**methods (line 1672)** — First batch:\n- **columns** — Full column chooser: saves column visibility/order to cookies, creates drag-reorderable checkbox panel with reset button.\n- **editButs** — Shows/hides/enables/disables toolbar buttons by name.\n- **readonly** — Sets datagrid to readonly (locks edit buttons).\n- **editDone** — Validates and ends current row edit.\n- **editFocus** — Begins editing a row (ends previous edit first).\n- **editAppend** — Adds a new row with auto-number support, `$autonum` expressions, `#selector` references, insert mode.\n- **tbar** — Creates Add/Insert/Edit/Delete/Save toolbar buttons with full CRUD behaviour.\n- **rowEditor** — Sets up full row editing with toolbar, before/after edit hooks.\n- **formedit** — Creates a dialog-based row editor: builds form from column editors, Save/Cancel/Delete buttons, readonly support.\n- **rowedit** — Sets up inline row editing with click-to-edit cells.\n- **showRow/hideRow** — Shows/hides individual rows by index.\n- **findRows** — Finds rows matching key-value criteria.\n- **showRows** — Filters visible rows by index array or key-value pair.\n- **editCell** — Edits a single cell (disables other editors temporarily).\n- **enableCellEdit** — Enables click-to-edit-cell mode.\n- **resizeColumn** — Programmatically resizes a column.\n\n**methods (line 2346)** — Second batch:\n- **dialog** — Creates a dynamic dialog editor from column definitions, with Save/Delete/Cancel.\n- **toExcel** — Exports datagrid to Excel (HTML table → base64 data URI download) with custom styling and DOM parsing.\n\n**defaults (line 2319)**:\n- `eidx:null, method:post, fit:true`.\n- `onBeforeLoad` — Builds URL from `_sqlid`.\n- `onBeforeEndEdit` — Returns true (hook point).\n- `onBeforeOpen` — Translates header text.\n\n**editors (line 2589)**:\n- `label` — Read-only label editor (renders HTML, no input).\n\n**view (line 2607)**:\n- `onAfterRender` — Adds `datagrid-sort` class to sortable column headers.\n\n### Tree (lines 2620-2772)\n**defaults (line 2622)**:\n- `locked:false, method:post`.\n- `keyHandler` — Forwards up/down/left/right keys from combotree to tree.\n- `formatter` — Renders node with optional `cls` class wrapper and `count` badge.\n- `onBeforeLoad` — Disables DnD and context menu in readonly mode.\n- `onBeforeSelect` — Blocks selection when locked.\n- `onCheck` — Sends ajax `upd` request when a checkbox is toggled (persists check state to server).\n\n**methods (line 2704)**:\n- **getLevel** — Returns tree indent level of a node.\n- **lock/unlock** — Locks/unlocks tree selection.\n- **move** — Moves a node up or down among siblings.\n- **getLeafs** — Returns all leaf nodes.\n- **setIcon/clearIcon** — Adds/removes icon class on a node.\n- **setFocus** — Selects and expands to a node by ID.\n- **getRoot** — Walks up parent chain to find root, or returns first root.\n\n### Multibox Widget (lines 2781-2982) — CUSTOM WIDGET\nA multi-select checkbox dropdown extending `$.fn.combo`:\n- Registers as parser plugin and form field type.\n- Creates a dropdown panel with checkboxes from data or `_sqlid` remote load.\n- Supports multi-column layout (1-4 columns), striped rows.\n- **setValue** — Checks/unchecks boxes matching comma-separated value string.\n- **setSelected** — Updates the hidden value and display text ("Selected Items (N)").\n- **onChecked** — Gathers checked values, updates value, fires `onSelect`.\n- Separator-configurable (default comma).'}
