2026-03-09 07:46:28,403 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'name': 'euiextend', 'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Investigate all overrides/enhancements in public/js/eui.extend.js, determine which are already in DUI, and incorporate missing ones.\n\n## Complete Override Inventory\n\n### Global Utilities (eui.*)\n- eui.aliases() — Copies textbox values between fields linked by data-alias attributes. Called after form load.\n- eui.table(head, rows) — Builds HTML table from column defs and row data.\n- eui.colsort(dg, arr) — Reorders datagrid columns in DOM to match an array of field names.\n- eui.droplist(ul, cb) — Makes li items draggable/droppable for reordering (used in column chooser).\n- eui.translate(obj) — i18n: replaces element text with translation from dwap.lang dictionary.\n- eui.formatValue(target) — Applies a textbox\'s formatter function to its current value.\n- eui.date(val) — Extracts date portion (digits and hyphens) from a string.\n- eui.ref2text(val) — Converts ^ separators to . in reference strings.\n- eui.currency(val) — Formats number as $X.XX.\n- eui.integer(val) — Formats number as fixed-decimal.\n- eui.number(val) — Parses and formats to 2 decimal places.\n- eui.isloading(fid) — Returns whether a form is currently loading data.\n- eui.toolbar(els) — Dynamically builds toolbar items in the panel header.\n- eui.textPut(obj) — Batch-sets textbox values by ID from an object.\n- eui.textGet(arr) — Batch-gets textbox values by ID into an object.\n- eui.sqlid(sqlid) — Resolves _sqlid to a URL, prepending menu root if single-part.\n- eui.navi(cbo) — Appends forward/back nav buttons to a combobox.\n- eui.eventOff(obj, type, evt) — Temporarily disables a widget event handler.\n- eui.eventOn(obj, type, evt) — Re-enables a previously disabled event handler.\n\n### Parser — COMMENTED OUT\n- $.parser.onComplete — Would iterate datagrids after parse. Disabled.\n\n### Panel\n- panel.defaults.loadingMessage — Set to \'\' (suppresses "Loading..." text).\n- panel.methods.setIcon — Adds an icon CSS class to the panel icon element.\n\n### Dialog\n- dialog.parseOptions — COMMENTED OUT (would add dialog-box class).\n- dialog.defaults.bodyCls — Set to \'dbox\' on all dialogs.\n\n### Window\n- window.defaults — Forces modal-only: closable:true, collapsible:false, minimizable:false, maximizable:false, modal:true.\n\n### Tabs\n- tabs.defaults.onUpdate — Translates tab titles, enables buttons on first tab.\n- tabs.defaults.onUnselect — Prevents tab switch if locked; triggers button state management.\n- tabs.methods.onDemand — Lazy-loads tab content from template fragments on first select.\n- tabs.methods.enableAll — Enables all tabs at once, optionally selects one.\n- tabs.methods.disableAll — Disables all tabs at once, optionally selects one.\n- tabs.methods.lock — Prevents tab switching via locked flag.\n- tabs.methods.unlock — Allows tab switching again.\n\n### Form — MAJOR\n- form.parseOptions — Sets ajax method. .single forms: mode=upd, builds URL from _sqlid, auto-loads if .load class. .multi forms: mode=add, disables .fkey fields.\n- form.defaults.onChange — Tracks changed fields in array, adds .changed class, fires changed event. Skips during loading.\n- form.defaults.onSubmit — Blocks if read-only, validates (finds hidden invalid fields in tabs), alerts on failure.\n- form.defaults.success — Parses JSON; del mode resets+reloads combo; add/upd resets editbox or QBE; fires done/success events.\n- form.defaults.onBeforeLoad — Clears change tracking, sets loading flag.\n- form.defaults.onLoadSuccess — Enables/disables form per read-only, unlocks tabs, stores fkey, calls aliases(), fires loadDone after 250ms.\n- form.methods.reload — Reloads form data using _sqlid and current fkey value.\n- form.methods.reset — Resets all field types (not just native inputs).\n- form.methods.getData — Returns form data as key-value dictionary.\n- form.methods.focusFirst — Focuses first enabled visible non-readonly input.\n- form.methods.unchange — Clears .changed class and resets change tracking.\n- form.methods.preload — Loads data without triggering onLoadSuccess.\n- form.methods.changeFieldName — Renames all field name/textboxName attributes via transform function.\n- form.methods.reselect — Re-selects all comboboxes in form (EUI 1.4.1 bug workaround).\n- form.methods.enable — Removes form-lock class, clears .unlock on items.\n- form.methods.disable — Adds form-lock class, unlocks .fkey items.\n\n### Linkbutton\n- linkbutton.parseOptions — Double-click prevention: locks button for clickms ms (default 2000) after mouseup.\n- linkbutton.defaults.onClick — Dispatches but_add()/but_clr() based on button ID.\n\n### Switchbutton — COMMENTED OUT\n- switchbutton.defaults — Would set onText:\'YES\', offText:\'NO\'. Disabled.\n\n### Date/Time Widgets\n- timespinner.defaults — highlight:1, value:\'12:00\'.\n- datetimebox.defaults.formatter — Formats via myTime().\n- datetimebox.defaults.parser — Parses ISO strings with timezone offset correction.\n- datebox.defaults._sharedCalendar — Uses shared #calendar element.\n- datebox.defaults.formatter — Formats via myDate().\n- datebox.defaults.parser — Handles 6-digit dates, ISO conversion.\n- datebox.defaults.onChange — Validates against postdate/predate flags (blocks future/past dates).\n- datebox.methods.getDate — Parses current value to Date object.\n- datebox.methods.today — Sets or returns today\'s formatted date.\n- datebox.methods.month — Sets or returns 1st of current month.\n- datebox.methods.year — Sets or returns Jan 1 of current year.\n- datetimebox.methods.getTime — Parses datetime value to Date object.\n- datebox.parseOptions — Auto-sets value to today/month/year based on .today/.month/.year class.\n\n### Number/Spinner\n- numberspinner.defaults — editable:true, min:0, precision:2.\n- numberbox.methods.set — Batch-sets numberbox options and re-applies current value.\n\n### Textbox / Validation\n- validatebox.defaults.deltaX — Set to 20 (tooltip X offset).\n- Focus handler / initValue — COMMENTED OUT.\n- Validate parser — COMMENTED OUT.\n- validatebox.methods.required — Dynamically sets required flag and revalidates.\n- validatebox.methods.editable — Dynamically sets editable flag and revalidates.\n- textbox.methods.setValidType — Changes validType on textbox\'s inner validatebox.\n- textbox.methods.dropbox — Enables drag-and-drop file reading into textbox.\n\n### Validation Rules\n- csn — Comma-separated numbers only.\n- neq — Value must not equal a given parameter.\n- isJSON — Must be valid JSON.\n- noList — Always passes (placeholder).\n- inList — Value must match a combobox item\'s text.\n- sqlsafe — Only allows uppercase letters, digits, hyphens, slashes, dots, backslashes.\n- xlsx — Must end in .xlsx.\n- file — No dots, asterisks, or spaces.\n- udfLabels — Strips {...} prefix and *, checks remaining length.\n\n### Combobox parseOptions — MAJOR\n- fkey data — Stores combo reference on parent form.\n- .first/.last class — Auto-selects first or last item on load.\n- .edit class — Creates inline add/edit dialog for combo items with dynamic fields.\n- .fit class — Sets panelWidth:208.\n- .fkey class — Builds edit-wrap with validatebox for new record entry, nav buttons, sqlsafe validation.\n- .navi class — Appends forward/back navigation buttons.\n- cloneSource option — Clones data from another combobox.\n\n### Combobox defaults\n- Standard config — valueField:\'value\', textField:\'text\', method:\'post\', selectOnNavigation:false, validType:[\'inList\'].\n- onShowPanel/onHidePanel — Tracks clicked state flag.\n- onResize — Applies icon background, enables sticky group headers, starts auto-refresh interval.\n- loadFilter — Prepends "- ALL -" empty row for .all class combos.\n- onSelect — Triggers form load via formLoad(), fires select event.\n- onBeforeLoad — Builds URL from _sqlid, prevents double-loading via loaded flag.\n- onLoadSuccess — Auto-selects value if autoload option is set.\n\n### Combobox methods\n- paginate/_paginate — Infinite scroll loading with remote data.\n- cloneFrom — Clones combo data and state from another combobox.\n- reset — Resets to originalValue if not manually selected.\n- selected — Finds and selects item with selected:true in data.\n- filtertip — Creates filter tooltip with checkboxes modifying query params, saves to cookies.\n- delete — Removes combo item from data and DOM by value.\n- append — Adds new item to data and renders in panel.\n- sticky — Makes group headers sticky during scroll.\n- formLoad — Core: when fkey combo selects, loads parent form with that record from server.\n- empty — Clears all combo data.\n- toCombo — Restores combo to dropdown mode.\n- toText — Converts combo to plain text input (hides dropdown, removes inList).\n- getField — Gets a specific field from selected record.\n- load — Extends query params and reloads.\n- reload — Reloads with loaded:false reset, preserves selection via autoload.\n- find — Searches data for record matching key-value pair.\n- selectKey — Finds and selects item by key-value pair.\n- exists — Returns true/false if value exists in data.\n- reselect — Unselects then re-selects current value to retrigger events.\n- getRec — Returns full data record for current selection.\n- index — Navigates to next/previous item (used by nav buttons).\n- autonum — Toggles auto-number mode (readonly + auto-generated values).\n- editbox — Toggles between combo selection and text input for new record entry.\n\n### Datagrid methods — MAJOR\n- columns — Full column chooser: saves visibility/order to cookies, drag-reorderable panel, reset.\n- editButs — Shows/hides/enables/disables toolbar CRUD buttons by name.\n- readonly — Sets datagrid to readonly (locks edit buttons).\n- editDone — Validates current row and ends editing.\n- editFocus — Begins editing a row (ends previous first).\n- editAppend — Adds new row with $autonum expressions, #selector refs, insert mode.\n- tbar — Creates Add/Insert/Edit/Delete/Save toolbar with full CRUD wiring.\n- rowEditor — Sets up row editing with toolbar, before/after edit hooks.\n- formedit — Creates dialog-based row editor from column editors, Save/Cancel/Delete.\n- rowedit — Sets up inline click-to-edit row editing.\n- showRow/hideRow — Shows/hides individual rows by index.\n- findRows — Finds rows matching key-value criteria, returns rows and indices.\n- showRows — Filters visible rows by index or key-value, returns counts.\n- editCell — Edits single cell (temporarily disables other column editors).\n- enableCellEdit — Enables click-to-edit-cell mode for whole grid.\n- resizeColumn — Programmatically resizes a column by field name.\n- dialog — Creates dynamic dialog editor from column definitions.\n- toExcel — Exports datagrid to Excel via HTML table → base64 data URI download.\n\n### Datagrid defaults\n- eidx, method, fit — null, \'post\', true.\n- onBeforeLoad — Builds URL from _sqlid attribute.\n- onBeforeEndEdit — Returns true (hook point).\n- onBeforeOpen — Translates header text.\n\n### Datagrid editors\n- label — Read-only label editor (renders HTML, no input).\n\n### Datagrid view\n- onAfterRender — Adds datagrid-sort CSS class to sortable column headers.\n\n### Tree defaults\n- locked, method — false, \'post\'.\n- keyHandler — Forwards up/down/left/right keys from combotree to tree.\n- formatter — Renders node with optional cls class wrapper and count badge.\n- onBeforeLoad — Disables DnD and context menu in readonly mode.\n- onBeforeSelect — Blocks selection when locked.\n- onCheck — Sends ajax upd request to persist checkbox state to server.\n\n### Tree methods\n- getLevel — Returns indent level of a tree node.\n- lock/unlock — Locks/unlocks tree selection.\n- move — Moves node up or down among siblings.\n- getLeafs — Returns all leaf nodes.\n- setIcon/clearIcon — Adds/removes icon CSS class on a node.\n- setFocus — Selects node by ID and expands tree path to it.\n- getRoot — Walks up parent chain to find root, or returns first root.\n\n### Multibox — CUSTOM WIDGET\n- Registration — EUI parser plugin and form field type.\n- Panel — Dropdown with checkboxes from local data or _sqlid remote load.\n- Layout — 1-4 column layout, optional striped rows.\n- setValue — Checks/unchecks boxes matching comma-separated value string.\n- setSelected — Updates hidden value and display text ("Selected Items (N)").\n- onChecked — Gathers checked values, updates value, fires onSelect.\n- Config — Separator-configurable (default comma), required, editable, prompt options.'}
