2026-03-09 07:51:23,784 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'text': 'Classify each eui.* utility — needed in DUI? If so, where?\n\n- eui.aliases() — Copies values between fields via data-alias. Needed? Do any DUI pages use data-alias?\n- eui.table(head, rows) — Builds ad-hoc HTML table. Needed? Or does DUI use Pug templates for this?\n- eui.colsort(dg, arr) — Reorders datagrid columns in DOM. Needed? DUI datagrid handles column order differently?\n- eui.droplist(ul, cb) — Drag/drop reorder for li items. Needed? Used by column chooser — does DUI have equivalent?\n- eui.translate(obj) — i18n text replacement from dwap.lang. Needed? Does DUI handle i18n differently?\n- eui.formatValue(target) — Applies formatter to textbox value. Needed? DUI inputs have their own formatting?\n- eui.date(val) — Extracts date from string. Needed? Simple utility, could go in $.dui namespace.\n- eui.ref2text(val) — Converts ^ to . in refs. Needed? Used in display formatting.\n- eui.currency/integer/number(val) — Number formatters. Needed? DUI may have formatters already.\n- eui.isloading(fid) — Checks form loading state. Needed? DUI form plugin tracks loading?\n- eui.toolbar(els) — Dynamic toolbar builder. Needed? DUI has toolbar mixin in Pug.\n- eui.textPut/textGet — Batch get/set by ID. Needed? DUI equivalent via $.dui or $.page.fn?\n- eui.sqlid(sqlid) — Resolves _sqlid to URL. Needed? Core data plumbing — likely already in DUI.\n- eui.navi(cbo) — Nav buttons for combobox. Needed? DUI combobox plugin handles nav?\n- eui.eventOff/eventOn — Temp disable/enable event handlers. Needed? Generic utility pattern.'}
2026-03-09 07:51:25,768 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'text': "Classify Panel overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- panel.defaults.loadingMessage = '' — Suppresses loading text. Needed? DUI doesn't use EUI panels — N/A?\n- panel.methods.setIcon — Adds icon class to panel. Needed? DUI doesn't use EUI panels — N/A?"}
2026-03-09 07:51:28,602 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 4, 'text': "Classify Dialog/Window overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- dialog.parseOptions — COMMENTED OUT. Skip.\n- dialog.defaults.bodyCls = 'dbox' — Adds class to dialog body. Needed? DUI uses modal-plugin.js with DaisyUI modal component.\n- window.defaults — Forces modal-only (no minimize/maximize/collapse). Needed? DUI modals are already modal-only by design."}
2026-03-09 07:51:33,042 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 5, 'text': 'Classify Tabs overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- tabs.defaults.onUpdate — Translates tab titles, enables buttons on first tab. Needed? DUI tabs are native HTML, i18n handled differently?\n- tabs.defaults.onUnselect — Prevents switch if locked, manages button state. Needed? Tab locking behaviour needed in DUI?\n- tabs.methods.onDemand — Lazy-loads content from template on first select. Needed? DUI could benefit from lazy tab loading.\n- tabs.methods.enableAll/disableAll — Batch enable/disable tabs. Needed? Utility for multi-tab forms.\n- tabs.methods.lock/unlock — Prevents/allows tab switching. Needed? Used to keep user on a tab during edits.'}
2026-03-09 07:51:45,689 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 6, 'text': 'Classify Form overrides — needed in DUI? MAJOR section.\n\nparseOptions:\n- Sets ajax method. Needed? DUI form-plugin handles submit method.\n- .single/.multi form class handling (mode, asdpx, _sqlid URL, auto-load). Needed? Core form behaviour — DUI form-plugin likely reimplements this.\n\ndefaults:\n- onChange — Track changed fields, .changed class, skip during loading. Needed? DUI form-plugin has dirty tracking?\n- onSubmit — Read-only block, validation with hidden-tab-field detection. Needed? Validation logic is critical.\n- success — JSON parse, del/add/upd mode handling, editbox reset, events. Needed? Core CRUD response handler.\n- onBeforeLoad — Clear changes, set loading flag. Needed? Loading state management.\n- onLoadSuccess — Enable/disable per read-only, unlock tabs, aliases, loadDone event. Needed? Post-load lifecycle.\n\nmethods:\n- reload — Reload via _sqlid + fkey. Needed? Core data operation.\n- reset — Reset all field types. Needed? DUI form-plugin has reset?\n- getData — Form to dictionary. Needed? DUI likely has equivalent.\n- focusFirst — Focus first editable input. Needed? UX convenience.\n- unchange — Clear dirty tracking. Needed? Pairs with onChange.\n- preload — Load without triggering onLoadSuccess. Needed? Used for pre-populating forms.\n- changeFieldName — Rename fields via transform. Needed? Niche but used.\n- reselect — Re-select all combos (EUI 1.4.1 bug). Needed? EUI-specific bug workaround — likely N/A.\n- enable/disable — Form lock/unlock with CSS class. Needed? Read-only form state.'}
2026-03-09 07:51:49,046 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 7, 'text': 'Classify Linkbutton overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- linkbutton.parseOptions — Double-click prevention (2s lock after mouseup). Needed? Good UX pattern — DUI buttons could use this. Where: button click handlers or a utility.\n- linkbutton.defaults.onClick — Dispatches but_add()/but_clr() by button ID. Needed? EUI-specific button dispatch — DUI uses different button wiring.'}
2026-03-09 07:51:56,405 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 8, 'text': "Classify Date/Time Widget overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- timespinner.defaults (highlight:1, value:'12:00') — EUI widget defaults. Needed? DUI uses native HTML time inputs or DaisyUI equivalents.\n- datetimebox.defaults.formatter/parser — Custom datetime formatting and ISO/timezone parsing. Needed? The formatting/parsing logic is needed — DUI date inputs need consistent format.\n- datebox.defaults._sharedCalendar — Shared calendar element. Needed? EUI-specific optimisation — N/A for DUI.\n- datebox.defaults.formatter/parser — Date formatting and 6-digit/ISO parsing. Needed? Date format logic is needed.\n- datebox.defaults.onChange — Pre/post date validation. Needed? Business rule — should be in DUI if date restrictions are used.\n- datebox.methods.getDate/today/month/year — Date helpers. Needed? Utility functions for date fields.\n- datetimebox.methods.getTime — Parse to Date. Needed? Utility.\n- datebox.parseOptions — Auto-set from .today/.month/.year class. Needed? Convenience classes — DUI could use data attributes or Pug mixin params instead."}
2026-03-09 07:51:58,249 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 9, 'text': 'Classify Number/Spinner overrides — needed in DUI?\n\n- numberspinner.defaults (editable:true, min:0, precision:2) — EUI widget defaults. Needed? DUI uses native number inputs — defaults set via Pug mixin params.\n- numberbox.methods.set — Batch-set options and re-apply value. Needed? Niche utility — DUI number inputs are simpler.'}
2026-03-09 07:52:07,737 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 10, 'text': 'Classify Textbox/Validation/Rules overrides — needed in DUI?\n\nTextbox/Validation:\n- validatebox.defaults.deltaX = 20 — Tooltip offset. Needed? EUI-specific — N/A.\n- Focus handler / initValue — COMMENTED OUT. Skip.\n- Validate parser — COMMENTED OUT. Skip.\n- validatebox.methods.required/editable — Dynamic required/editable toggle. Needed? DUI can use native HTML required attribute + JS.\n- textbox.methods.setValidType — Change validation type at runtime. Needed? DUI validation is different (HTML5 + custom).\n- textbox.methods.dropbox — Drag-and-drop file reading. Needed? Niche feature — check if any DUI page uses it.\n\nValidation Rules (9 rules):\n- csn — Comma-separated numbers. Needed? Check if any page uses this rule.\n- neq — Not equal to param. Needed? Check usage.\n- isJSON — Valid JSON check. Needed? Used in config editors.\n- noList — Always passes. Needed? Placeholder — probably not.\n- inList — Must match combobox item. Needed? Core combo validation — DUI combobox handles this differently?\n- sqlsafe — Restricted character set. Needed? Used on fkey fields — security/data integrity rule.\n- xlsx — Must end .xlsx. Needed? Check usage.\n- file — No dots/asterisks/spaces. Needed? Check usage.\n- udfLabels — Strip prefix, check length. Needed? UDF-specific — check if DUI has UDF pages.'}
2026-03-09 07:52:22,779 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 11, 'text': 'Classify Combobox overrides — needed in DUI? MAJOR section.\n\nparseOptions:\n- fkey data storage on form — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin tracks fkey differently.\n- .first/.last auto-select — Needed? Convenience — could be a data attribute in DUI.\n- .edit class (inline add/edit dialog) — Needed? Complex feature — check if DUI pages use editable combos.\n- .fit class (panelWidth) — Needed? EUI-specific layout — N/A.\n- .fkey class (edit-wrap, nav buttons, sqlsafe) — Needed? Core record selection pattern — DUI has its own fkey/searchbox.\n- .navi class (forward/back buttons) — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin has nav?\n- cloneSource — Needed? Check if any DUI page clones combos.\n\ndefaults:\n- Standard config (value/text fields, post, inList) — Needed? DUI combobox has own defaults.\n- onShowPanel/onHidePanel clicked tracking — Needed? EUI panel behaviour — N/A.\n- onResize (icon bg, sticky groups, auto-refresh) — Needed? Mixed: icon bg maybe, sticky groups yes, auto-refresh yes.\n- loadFilter (ALL row) — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin has this?\n- onSelect → formLoad — Needed? Core behaviour — DUI combobox-plugin handles select→load.\n- onBeforeLoad (_sqlid URL, loaded flag) — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin handles data loading.\n- onLoadSuccess (autoload) — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin has auto-select?\n\nmethods (22):\n- paginate/_paginate — Needed? Infinite scroll — check if DUI needs this.\n- cloneFrom — Needed? Check usage.\n- reset — Needed? DUI combobox has reset?\n- selected — Needed? Auto-select marked item.\n- filtertip — Needed? Complex filter UI — check if DUI pages use it.\n- delete/append — Needed? Direct item manipulation.\n- sticky — Needed? Group header stickiness.\n- formLoad — Needed? Core fkey→form load — DUI has this in combobox-plugin.\n- empty — Needed? Clear combo data.\n- toCombo/toText — Needed? Mode toggle — check if DUI pages use this.\n- getField — Needed? Get field from selected record.\n- load/reload — Needed? DUI combobox-plugin has reload.\n- find/selectKey/exists — Needed? Data search utilities.\n- reselect — Needed? Event retrigger.\n- getRec — Needed? Get full record.\n- index — Needed? Nav button support — DUI combobox-plugin has nav.\n- autonum — Needed? Auto-number mode.\n- editbox — Needed? Toggle combo/text for new record entry.'}
2026-03-09 07:52:35,141 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 12, 'text': 'Classify Datagrid overrides — needed in DUI? MAJOR section.\n\nmethods (18):\n- columns — Column chooser with cookie persistence, drag reorder. Needed? DUI datagrid-plugin has column management?\n- editButs — Show/hide/enable/disable CRUD toolbar buttons. Needed? DUI datagrid toolbar works differently.\n- readonly — Lock edit buttons. Needed? Read-only grid state.\n- editDone — Validate and end row edit. Needed? DUI inline editing.\n- editFocus — Begin editing row. Needed? DUI inline editing.\n- editAppend — Add row with $autonum, #selector, insert mode. Needed? Core add-row behaviour.\n- tbar — CRUD toolbar creation. Needed? DUI datagrid-plugin has toolbar?\n- rowEditor — Full row editing setup. Needed? DUI inline editing pattern.\n- formedit — Dialog-based row editor. Needed? DUI datagrid editing via modal.\n- rowedit — Click-to-edit inline rows. Needed? DUI inline editing.\n- showRow/hideRow — Show/hide rows by index. Needed? Row filtering.\n- findRows — Find rows by key-value. Needed? Data search.\n- showRows — Filter visible rows. Needed? Client-side filtering.\n- editCell — Single cell editing. Needed? Cell-level editing.\n- enableCellEdit — Click-to-edit-cell mode. Needed? Cell editing mode.\n- resizeColumn — Programmatic column resize. Needed? Check usage.\n- dialog — Dynamic dialog editor from columns. Needed? Alternative edit UI.\n- toExcel — Export to Excel. Needed? Reporting feature — likely needed.\n\ndefaults:\n- eidx, method, fit — Base config. Needed? DUI datagrid has own defaults.\n- onBeforeLoad (_sqlid URL) — Needed? DUI datagrid handles data loading.\n- onBeforeEndEdit (hook) — Needed? Edit lifecycle hook.\n- onBeforeOpen (translate headers) — Needed? i18n.\n\neditors:\n- label — Read-only HTML label editor. Needed? Display-only column.\n\nview:\n- onAfterRender (sort class on headers) — Needed? Visual sort indicator.'}
2026-03-09 07:52:43,540 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 13, 'text': 'Classify Tree and Multibox overrides — needed in DUI?\n\nTREE defaults:\n- locked, method — Base config. Needed? DUI tree component?\n- keyHandler (forward keys from combotree) — Needed? Only if DUI has combotree.\n- formatter (cls wrapper, count badge) — Needed? Tree node rendering.\n- onBeforeLoad (disable DnD/context menu in readonly) — Needed? Read-only tree.\n- onBeforeSelect (block when locked) — Needed? Lock pattern.\n- onCheck (ajax persist checkbox state) — Needed? Server-side checkbox persistence.\n\nTREE methods:\n- getLevel — Node indent level. Needed? Tree utilities.\n- lock/unlock — Lock/unlock selection. Needed? Edit control.\n- move — Move node up/down. Needed? Tree reordering.\n- getLeafs — Get leaf nodes. Needed? Tree traversal.\n- setIcon/clearIcon — Node icon management. Needed? Visual state.\n- setFocus — Select + expand to node by ID. Needed? Programmatic navigation.\n- getRoot — Find root node. Needed? Tree traversal.\n\nMULTIBOX:\n- Entire custom widget (multi-select checkbox dropdown). Needed? Check if any DUI pages need multi-select. If so, could be a DUI plugin or use DaisyUI dropdown + checkboxes.\n- setValue/setSelected — Value management. Needed? Part of the widget.\n- onChecked — Event handling. Needed? Part of the widget.\n- Config (columns, striped, separator) — Layout options. Needed? Part of the widget.'}
