2026-03-09 07:54:26,597 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 2, 'id': 663, 'text': "## Classification — Global Utilities (eui.*)\n\n### ALREADY IN DUI\n- eui.aliases() → refreshAliases() in form-plugin.js:149. DUI version is more robust (handles select/textarea, scoped to form, try/catch).\n- eui.table() → $.dui.fmt.table in form-plugin.js:1525. Exact port of the EUI version.\n- eui.date() → $.dui.fmt.date in form-plugin.js:1510. Same logic. Also shimmed in dui-helpers.js:10.\n- eui.ref2text() → $.dui.fmt.ref2text in form-plugin.js:1546. Same logic.\n- eui.currency() → $.dui.fmt.currency in form-plugin.js:1513. Same logic. Also shimmed in dui-helpers.js:27.\n- eui.integer() → $.dui.fmt.integer in form-plugin.js:1516. Same logic.\n- eui.number() → $.dui.fmt.number in form-plugin.js:1519. Same logic. Also shimmed in dui-helpers.js:19.\n- eui.isloading() → $.dui.loading / opts.loading in form-plugin.js:317-320. DUI tracks loading state on $.dui and $.page.state.\n- eui.sqlid() → DUI datagrid-plugin builds URLs from _sqlid directly (datagrid-plugin.js:289). Searchbox-plugin also resolves _sqlid (searchbox-plugin.js:617-619). No standalone utility but logic is embedded where needed.\n- eui.toolbar() → DUI has toolbar-plugin.js and Pug toolbar mixin. Toolbar is declarative in DUI, not dynamically built from JS.\n\n### NOT NEEDED IN DUI\n- eui.colsort() — EUI DOM manipulation for column reorder. DUI datagrid handles columns via JSON config, not DOM reorder.\n- eui.droplist() — Drag/drop reorder for EUI column chooser. DUI doesn't use this pattern.\n- eui.translate() — i18n via dwap.lang dictionary. DUI does not currently use client-side i18n; labels are in Pug templates.\n- eui.formatValue() — Applies EUI textbox formatter. DUI inputs use native HTML + CSS formatting, not widget formatters.\n- eui.navi() — Appends nav buttons to EUI combobox. DUI searchbox-plugin has its own nav (highlight navigation, searchbox-plugin.js:343).\n- eui.eventOff/eventOn — Temp disable/enable EUI widget event handlers. DUI uses different event patterns (native DOM events, not widget options).\n- eui.textPut/textGet — Batch get/set via EUI textbox('getValue'). DUI uses native DOM .value or form-plugin getData/loadData.\n- eui.reselect — EUI 1.4.1 bug workaround. Not applicable.\n\n### VERDICT\nAll 19 utilities are either already ported to DUI or not needed. No items require porting."}
