2026-03-09 07:54:58,871 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 3, 'id': 664, 'text': "## Classification — Panel\n\n### NOT NEEDED IN DUI\n- panel.defaults.loadingMessage = '' — DUI panel-plugin.js:296 already has loadingMessage:'Loading...' as default. EUI override suppressed it; DUI keeps it. Different design choice, not a missing feature.\n- panel.methods.setIcon — EUI-specific panel icon API. DUI panel-plugin has no setIcon but uses Lucide icons via $.dui.icon(). Not needed — DUI uses different icon system.\n\n### VERDICT\nBoth items are N/A. No porting needed."}
2026-03-09 07:55:03,210 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 4, 'id': 665, 'text': "## Classification — Dialog / Window\n\n### NOT NEEDED IN DUI\n- dialog.parseOptions — COMMENTED OUT in EUI. Skip.\n- dialog.defaults.bodyCls = 'dbox' — EUI styling class. DUI modal-plugin uses native <dialog> with DaisyUI modal structure (modal-box class). N/A.\n- window.defaults (modal-only) — DUI modal-plugin already uses native <dialog>.showModal() which is inherently modal. No minimize/maximize/collapse exists. Already the default behaviour.\n\n### VERDICT\nAll items are N/A. DUI modal-plugin.js already covers the intent (modal-only dialogs, DaisyUI styling). No porting needed."}
