2026-03-09 07:59:54,998 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': "**Classification — Date/Time Widgets (8 items)**\n\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | timespinner defaults (highlight:1, value:'12:00') | ✅ Already | timespinner-plugin has defaults, uses native time input |\n| 2 | datetimebox defaults (formatter/parser/currentText) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native input[type=datetime-local], no datetimebox widget |\n| 3 | datetimebox methods.getTime | ❌ Not needed | No datetimebox in DUI |\n| 4 | datebox defaults (formatter/parser) | ✅ Already | datebox-plugin has formatter/parser with ISO handling |\n| 5 | datebox defaults sharedCalendar | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native date picker |\n| 6 | datebox defaults onChange (pre/post date validation) | ❌ Not needed | Can use min/max attributes on native date input. Page scripts can add own onChange. |\n| 7 | datebox methods (getDate/today/month/year) | ✅ Already | datebox-plugin has all four methods |\n| 8 | datebox parseOptions (.today/.month/.year class) | ✅ Already | datebox-plugin setTodayIfEmpty() handles these classes |\n\n**Result: No porting needed. 4 already in DUI, 4 not needed.**"}
