2026-03-09 08:00:22,362 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': '**Classification — Textbox / Validation / Rules (16 items)**\n\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | validatebox.defaults.deltaX=20 | ❌ Not needed | EUI tooltip positioning — DUI uses native validation + input-error class |\n| 2 | Focus handler / initValue | ❌ Not needed | COMMENTED OUT in EUI — never active |\n| 3 | Validate parser | ❌ Not needed | COMMENTED OUT in EUI — never active |\n| 4 | validatebox.methods.required | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin has required() method |\n| 5 | validatebox.methods.editable | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native readonly/disabled attributes |\n| 6 | textbox.methods.setValidType | ❌ Not needed | DUI validation uses data-options or direct opts — no runtime type change needed |\n| 7 | textbox.methods.dropbox | ❌ Not needed | Niche file-drop on textbox — very few pages, can be page-level JS |\n| 8 | rule: csn | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.csn |\n| 9 | rule: neq | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.neq |\n| 10 | rule: isJSON | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.isJSON |\n| 11 | rule: noList | ❌ Not needed | Always-pass placeholder — no functional value |\n| 12 | rule: inList | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.inList (adapted for native select) |\n| 13 | rule: sqlsafe | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.sqlsafe |\n| 14 | rule: xlsx | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.xlsx |\n| 15 | rule: file | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.file |\n| 16 | rule: udfLabels | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.udfLabels |\n\n**Result: No porting needed. 9 already in DUI, 7 not needed.**'}
