2026-03-09 08:00:52,304 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': "**Classification — Combobox (30 items)**\n\n**parseOptions (7 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | fkey data storage on form | ❌ Not needed | EUI-specific DOM tracking |\n| 2 | .first/.last auto-select on load | ⚠️ Missing | Low priority — only a few combos use this. Could add as data attribute. |\n| 3 | .edit class (inline JSON editor combo) | ❌ Not needed | Very niche — only used for config editing combos |\n| 4 | .fit class (panelWidth) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native select — no panel |\n| 5 | .fkey class (editbox, nav, validation) | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has editbox, nav buttons, template-based approach |\n| 6 | .navi class (fwd/back buttons) | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has nav button wiring (lines 211-225) |\n| 7 | cloneSource | ❌ Not needed | EUI-specific widget cloning |\n\n**defaults (8 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 8 | queryParams, method, valueField, textField | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin defaults |\n| 9 | validType:['inList'] | ✅ Already | validatebox-plugin rules.inList |\n| 10 | autoload | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin handles autoload in loadData() |\n| 11 | onShowPanel/onHidePanel (clicked flag) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native select — no panel show/hide |\n| 12 | onResize (icon bg, sticky, auto-refresh) | ❌ Not needed | EUI widget resize events — N/A for native select |\n| 13 | loadFilter (.all row prepend) | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin loadFilter unwraps {rows:[]} |\n| 14 | onSelect → formLoad | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin defaults.onSelect calls formLoad |\n| 15 | onBeforeLoad (_sqlid, loaded flag) | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin request() handles _sqlid resolution |\n\n**methods (15 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 16 | paginate/_paginate | ❌ Not needed | EUI panel infinite scroll — DUI uses searchbox/QBE for large lists |\n| 17 | cloneFrom | ❌ Not needed | EUI-specific widget cloning |\n| 18 | reset | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has reset method |\n| 19 | selected | ❌ Not needed | EUI-specific auto-reselect from data |\n| 20 | filtertip | ❌ Not needed | Complex EUI tooltip filter — very niche |\n| 21 | delete/append | ❌ Not needed | EUI panel item manipulation — DUI rebuilds options via loadData |\n| 22 | sticky | ❌ Not needed | EUI group header sticking — no panel in DUI |\n| 23 | formLoad | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has formLoad method |\n| 24 | empty | ✅ Already | Equivalent to clear/loadData([]) |\n| 25 | toCombo/toText | ❌ Not needed | EUI-specific mode toggle — not used in DUI |\n| 26 | getField | ❌ Not needed | Can use getRec() then access field directly |\n| 27 | load/reload | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has reload method |\n| 28 | find/selectKey | ⚠️ Missing | find() searches data by key/val, selectKey finds+selects. Useful utility. Low priority — page scripts can iterate getData(). |\n| 29 | exists | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has exists method |\n| 30 | reselect | ❌ Not needed | EUI 1.4.1 bug workaround |\n| 31 | getRec | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has getRec method |\n| 32 | index | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin nav buttons handle index cycling |\n| 33 | autonum | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin editbox handles autonum (resolveAutonumValue) |\n| 34 | editbox | ✅ Already | combobox-plugin has full editbox method with template approach |\n\n**Result: 17 already in DUI, 11 not needed, 2 minor gaps (first/last auto-select, find/selectKey).**"}
