2026-03-09 08:01:37,436 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': "**Classification — Datagrid (22 items)**\n\n**methods (18 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | columns (column chooser + cookie persistence) | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin has columns() method (L1144) |\n| 2 | editButs (show/hide/enable/disable toolbar buttons) | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin has tbarEnable/tbarDisable (L205-208) |\n| 3 | readonly (lock edit buttons) | ⚠️ Missing | DUI datagrid has no readonly toggle. Low priority — form-level readonly handles most cases. |\n| 4 | editDone (validate + end edit) | ❌ Not needed | DUI datagrid uses different editing pattern (editor overlay, not inline row edit) |\n| 5 | editFocus (begin editing row) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses dblclick or toolbar to open editor |\n| 6 | editAppend (add row with autonum) | ❌ Not needed | DUI toolbar add button handles new rows via _btnAdd click handler |\n| 7 | tbar (CRUD toolbar creation) | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin creates toolbar buttons from Pug mixin templates |\n| 8 | rowEditor (full row editing setup) | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin has rowEditor method (L1185) |\n| 9 | formedit (dialog-based row editor) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses modal editor built from column config — different approach |\n| 10 | rowedit (click-to-edit inline) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses different editing UX |\n| 11 | showRow/hideRow | ❌ Not needed | DUI can use CSS display on tr elements directly |\n| 12 | findRows | ❌ Not needed | Page scripts can filter getRows() |\n| 13 | showRows (filter visible rows) | ❌ Not needed | Same as above |\n| 14 | editCell (single cell editing) | ❌ Not needed | DUI doesn't have cell-level editing |\n| 15 | enableCellEdit | ❌ Not needed | Same |\n| 16 | resizeColumn | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses CSS column widths |\n| 17 | dialog (dynamic dialog from columns) | ❌ Not needed | DUI rowEditor builds editor from column config |\n| 18 | toExcel (export to Excel) | ⚠️ Missing | Useful reporting feature. Would need DUI-specific implementation for HTML table export. |\n\n**defaults (4 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 19 | eidx, method, fit | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin has own defaults |\n| 20 | onBeforeLoad (_sqlid URL) | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin resolves _sqlid in init |\n| 21 | onBeforeEndEdit | ✅ Already | datagrid-plugin onEndEdit lifecycle |\n| 22 | onBeforeOpen (translate headers) | ❌ Not needed | DUI headers rendered by Pug mixin with i18n built in |\n\n**editors (1 item):**\n| 23 | label editor | ❌ Not needed | DUI columns render read-only by default |\n\n**view (1 item):**\n| 24 | onAfterRender (sort class on headers) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses data-sort attributes + CSS |\n\n**Result: 6 already in DUI, 14 not needed, 2 gaps (readonly toggle, toExcel).**"}
