2026-03-09 08:02:01,279 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'text': "**Classification — Tree / Multibox (20 items)**\n\n**TREE defaults (6 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | locked, method | ✅ Already | tree-plugin defaults: method:'post'. Lock via onBeforeSelect. |\n| 2 | keyHandler (combotree key forwarding) | ❌ Not needed | DUI has no combotree widget |\n| 3 | formatter (cls wrapper, count badge) | ⚠️ Missing | DUI tree formatter is plain `node.text`. EUI adds .cls wrapping and (count) badges. Low priority — page scripts can override formatter. |\n| 4 | onBeforeLoad (disable DnD/context in readonly) | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has disableDnd stub and onContextMenu support |\n| 5 | onBeforeSelect (block when locked) | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has onBeforeSelect callback |\n| 6 | onCheck (ajax persist checkbox) | ❌ Not needed | Business logic — page scripts handle their own check persistence |\n\n**TREE methods (7 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 7 | getLevel | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has getLevel method |\n| 8 | lock/unlock | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has lock/unlock methods (pointer-events-none) |\n| 9 | move (up/down) | ❌ Not needed | DUI tree has insert(before/after) — page scripts can combine pop+insert |\n| 10 | getLeafs | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has getLeafs method |\n| 11 | setIcon/clearIcon | ❌ Not needed | DUI tree update() method handles iconCls changes |\n| 12 | setFocus | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has setFocus (scrollIntoView) + select + expandTo |\n| 13 | getRoot | ✅ Already | tree-plugin has getRoot method (with ancestor traversal) |\n\n**MULTIBOX (7 items):**\n| # | EUI Override | Status | Notes |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 14 | Plugin registration (parser, fieldTypes) | ✅ Already | multibox-plugin registers with parser and form.fieldTypes |\n| 15 | create function (panel, data load) | ✅ Already | multibox-plugin uses native select[multiple] — simpler, no panel |\n| 16 | defaults (striped, columns, separator) | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native select[multiple] — no panel layout needed |\n| 17 | onChecked | ❌ Not needed | DUI uses native change event on select[multiple] |\n| 18 | setValue (parse comma-separated, check boxes) | ✅ Already | multibox-plugin setValue splits comma-separated string |\n| 19 | setSelected (update text prompt) | ✅ Already | multibox-plugin setValues sets array on select |\n| 20 | getValue (join to comma string) | ✅ Already | multibox-plugin getValue joins with comma |\n\n**Result: 10 already in DUI, 6 not needed, 1 minor gap (tree formatter with cls/count).**"}
