2026-03-09 09:04:23,362 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'goal', 'text': 'Audit all overrides/enhancements in public/js/eui.extend.js (~2985 lines, ~130 items) and determine which are already in DUI, which are not needed, and which need action (shim, migration-map entry, or implementation).\n\n**Source of truth:** yaml/euiextend.yaml — structured per-item with: purpose, category, type, dui_plugin, dui_equivalent, status, decision, impact, action, shim_target, migration_map, commented_out, pages.\n\n**Phase 1 (complete):** Classified all ~130 items across 12 component categories. Results: ~90 already in DUI, ~34 not needed, ~6 gaps.\n\n**Phase 2 (in progress):** Refining "not needed" classifications — for each item determine: truly not needed, noop deprecation shim, redirect to DUI method, or migration-map entry. Validating against actual page usage via grep. 8 items previously marked "not needed" found to be used by pages — reclassified as needs_review in YAML.'}
2026-03-09 09:04:38,457 2155867 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_task_notes_set args={'kind': 'plan', 'text': '## Plan\n\n**Source of truth:** yaml/euiextend.yaml\n\n### Phase 1: Classification (COMPLETE — steps 1-13)\nClassified all ~130 items from eui.extend.js. Per-item results now in YAML.\n\n### Phase 2: Page usage scan & action refinement (IN PROGRESS)\nFor every item in the YAML:\n1. Grep all page scripts (html/eui/, html/dui/, public/js/) for actual usage\n2. Populate the `pages` array with file:line references\n3. For each "not needed" item, refine the `action` field:\n   - `none` — truly dead, no page calls it, internal EUI plumbing\n   - `shim_noop` — callable method that could be called; add noop + console.warn deprecation\n   - `shim_to_dui` — callable method with a DUI equivalent; shim redirects + warns\n   - `migration_map` — add pattern to yaml/migrator/migration-map.yaml\n   - `implement` — missing feature that needs porting to a DUI plugin\n4. Update `impact` field: hard_error / silent_fail / behaviour_diff / none\n\n### Phase 3: Implement actions\nFor each item where action != none:\n- Add shims, migration-map entries, or implement missing features\n- Test on relevant pages\n\n### Phase 4: Verify\n- Confirm no regressions on migrated DUI pages'}
